---
title: Cheesy Creamy Cauliflower Pasta with Baby Spinach and Chives
description: Making the perfect mac 'n’ cheese starts with a creamy cheddar cheese sauce and a swirl of sour cream. Roasted cauliflower and a chive garnish add elegance to this everyday favourite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-creamy-cauliflower-pasta-eb873463.jpg
